<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Error | Crypto Market Insights Dashboard</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e 0%, #16213e 100%);
            color: #e6e6e6;
            line-height: 1.6;
            padding: 20px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            width: 100%;
            background: rgba(25, 25, 43, 0.8);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 40px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            border: 1px solid rgba(76, 201, 240, 0.2);
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        h1 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: #e94560;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .error-message {
            color: #ff6b6b;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        
        .back-btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #0f3460, #1a5a8d);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin-top: 20px;
            transition: background 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .back-btn:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #e94560, #ff6b81);
        }
        
        footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding: 20px;
            color: #a9a9b3;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            border-top: 1px solid #0f3460;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>❌ Error</h1>
        <div class="error-message">
            <p><%= message %></p>
        </div>
        <p>We encountered an issue while processing your request.</p>
        
        <a href="/" class="back-btn">← Back to Dashboard</a>
        
        <footer>
            <p>Powered by Jr (Junior) | Created for Jay | <%= new Date().getFullYear() %></p>
        </footer>
    </div>
</body>
</html>